{"tid":1630172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Empty R日日cut班，一開翻又炒","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:44:27.000Z","uid":313647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74fd394e4a39c5e879113d6d3d87244cf32e9f6a","tid":1630172,"uid":313647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵荔景站往美孚站列車撞到車擋，六人受傷，荃灣綫因此全綫暫停。<br />\n<br />\n列車停在管道內，車上當時有大批乘客，乘客由消防員協助離開車廂，沿管道疏散返回荔景站。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，一列開往美孚站的列車以慢速越過停車位置時觸及車擋，大批消防員到場處理，有六人受傷，其他乘客陸續離開車站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365315&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365315%26refer%3DShare&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6oZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=5836934a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365315%26refer%3DShare&h=195c58fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365315&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"155fcebe8952cca522192f1b29f608fcd846e21e","tid":1630172,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］全民起動 三罷民意調查<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們暫時收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6oZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=675d5cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n民調將於10月11日中午12時結束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFm4xnS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFm4xnS.jpg&h=eb050f34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dd660b043d4ce6d93bea533693ee7620e3ad1cb","tid":1630172,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"馬屎又話港鐵世界第一既，深潛啊而家<img src=\"/assets